            <h2>#AdoptLove</h2>
            <p>
                Approximately 1478 dogs & cats die every day on road in India. FurAngels is on a mission to provide every dog and cat a home before 2035.
                <br />It's just one of the many ways FurAngels gives back and helps you become a part of something larger. Join FurAngels Community
                <br />and help setting up Pet houses in your surrounding for strays.
