                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span>What is fee to adopt a pet?</span>
                    <span>&#9654;</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>No, there is no fee for pet adoption on Furangels. However, if you adopt from a different city pet owner/rescuer can ask for travel charges. In case if you find someone asking for charges you can write us at support@furangels.com.</p>
